  <entry>
    <title>我的第一篇博客文章</title>
    <url>/2026/04/16/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>美化博客</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h1 id="开启首页阅读全文模式，只显示摘要"><a href="#开启首页阅读全文模式，只显示摘要" class="headerlink" title="开启首页阅读全文模式，只显示摘要"></a>开启首页阅读全文模式，只显示摘要</h1><h2 id="config配置"><a href="#config配置" class="headerlink" title="config配置"></a>config配置</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 必须改成false！关闭自定义description摘要</span><br><span class="line">excerpt_description: false</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 保持true，开启阅读全文按钮</span><br><span class="line">read_more_btn: true</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="加截断符号"><a href="#加截断符号" class="headerlink" title="加截断符号"></a>加截断符号</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 加在文章中要隐藏的文字前面</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr>
<h1 id="开启打赏功能"><a href="#开启打赏功能" class="headerlink" title="开启打赏功能"></a>开启打赏功能</h1><h2 id="打开zh-CN文件，修改"><a href="#打开zh-CN文件，修改" class="headerlink" title="打开zh-CN文件，修改"></a>打开zh-CN文件，修改</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 文件位置</span><br><span class="line">blog\themes\next\languages\zh-CN.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/images/reward_config.png" alt="打赏文字修改方式"></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 开启打赏方式</span><br><span class="line">reward:</span><br><span class="line">  wechatpay: /images/wechatpay.jpg</span><br><span class="line">  alipay: /images/alipay.jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h1 id="开启动态背景"><a href="#开启动态背景" class="headerlink" title="开启动态背景"></a>开启动态背景</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 搜索canvas</span><br><span class="line">canvas_ribbon:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true    # 总开关：true开启彩带动画，false关闭完全隐藏</span><br><span class="line">  size: 300       # 彩带的宽度大小，数字越大彩带越宽</span><br><span class="line">  alpha: 0.6      # 彩带透明度：0完全透明看不见，1完全不透明实心，0.6半透明刚好好看</span><br><span class="line">  zIndex: -1      # 层级：-1代表彩带在网页最底层、背景后面，不会挡住文字、按钮、内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h1 id="给博客添加fork-github"><a href="#给博客添加fork-github" class="headerlink" title="给博客添加fork github"></a>给博客添加fork github</h1><h2 id="打开网址"><a href="#打开网址" class="headerlink" title="打开网址"></a>打开网址</h2><p><a href="https://tholman.com/github-corners/">github-corners</a><br><img src="/images/corners.png" alt="corners"><br><a href="https://github.blog/news-insights/github-ribbons/">github Ribbons</a><br><img src="/images/ribbons.png" alt="ribbons"></p>
<h2 id="添加corners至右上角"><a href="#添加corners至右上角" class="headerlink" title="添加corners至右上角"></a>添加corners至右上角</h2><h3 id="复制corners配置"><a href="#复制corners配置" class="headerlink" title="复制corners配置"></a>复制corners配置</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#打开配置文件，配置文件所在路径</span><br><span class="line">\blog\themes\next\layout\_layout.njk </span><br><span class="line">#找到这行，第20行，复制在这行的下一行</span><br><span class="line">&lt;div class=&quot;headband&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt; </span><br><span class="line"># 改为自己github路径</span><br><span class="line">&quot;https://your-url&quot; class=&quot;github-corner&quot; #原本示例链接</span><br><span class="line">&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.comm/lan666-y&quot; #自己github地址</span><br><span class="line">#保存刷新即可</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/images/corners_fig.png" alt="corners-fig"></p>
<hr>
<h1 id="修改文章内链接样式"><a href="#修改文章内链接样式" class="headerlink" title="修改文章内链接样式"></a>修改文章内链接样式</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 配置文件路径</span><br><span class="line">\blog\themes\next\source\css\_common\components\post\post-body.styl</span><br><span class="line"># 在文件最后加上以下函数</span><br><span class="line">.post-body p a&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  color: #345</span><br><span class="line">  border-bottom: none;</span><br><span class="line">  &amp;:hover&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    color: red;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr>
<h1 id="修改文章底部带-的标签"><a href="#修改文章底部带-的标签" class="headerlink" title="修改文章底部带#的标签"></a>修改文章底部带#的标签</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 配置文件路径</span><br><span class="line">\blog\themes\next\layout\_macro\post.njk</span><br><span class="line"># 增加配置，就会变成google的图标</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-google&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/images/tag_fig.png" alt="tag_fig"></p>
<hr>
<h1 id="增加来必立评论"><a href="#增加来必立评论" class="headerlink" title="增加来必立评论"></a>增加来必立评论</h1><h2 id="配置文件对应代码段"><a href="#配置文件对应代码段" class="headerlink" title="配置文件对应代码段"></a>配置文件对应代码段</h2><ul>
<li>选择默认加载哪个评论系统<br>active后面是空的，代表当前所有评论全部关闭，页面不会显示任何评论！<br>想启用Livere（来必力），改成 active: livere 即可。<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 多评论系统支持（核心功能：同时装多个评论插件，页面可以互相切换）</span><br><span class="line"># Multiple Comment System Support</span><br><span class="line">comments:</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: tabs | buttons # 评论切换控件样式，二选一：</span><br><span class="line">  # tabs = 标签页横向切换（你现在用的这个，最美观）</span><br><span class="line">  # buttons = 按钮方块切换</span><br><span class="line">  style: tabs</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  # Choose a comment system to be displayed by default.</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: disqus | disqusjs | livere | gitalk | utterances | isso</span><br><span class="line">  # 【核心配置】选择页面打开**默认自动加载**哪一个评论系统</span><br><span class="line">  # 可选值已经列出来了：disqus | disqusjs | livere | gitalk | utterances | isso</span><br><span class="line">  active:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  # Setting `true` means remembering the comment system selected by the visitor.</span><br><span class="line">  # 功能：是否记住访客上次选的评论插件</span><br><span class="line">  # true = 访客上次切到Gitalk，下次打开文章自动还是Gitalk</span><br><span class="line">  # false = 每次打开文章都强制重置成上面active设置的默认评论</span><br><span class="line">  storage: true</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  # Lazyload all comment systems.</span><br><span class="line">  # 功能：评论懒加载</span><br><span class="line">  # false = 页面打开立刻加载评论（你现在的设置）</span><br><span class="line">  # true = 滚动到文章底部才加载评论（优化首页加载速度，推荐改成true）</span><br><span class="line">  lazyload: false</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  # Modify texts or order for any naves, here are some examples.</span><br><span class="line">  # 自定义每个评论插件：页面显示文字、排序先后顺序</span><br><span class="line">  nav:</span><br><span class="line">    #disqus:</span><br><span class="line">    #  text: Load Disqus  # 页面上这个按钮显示的文字</span><br><span class="line">    #  order: -1        # 排序优先级，数字越小越靠左排</span><br><span class="line">    #gitalk:</span><br><span class="line">    #  order: -2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="livere评论配置"><a href="#livere评论配置" class="headerlink" title="livere评论配置"></a>livere评论配置</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># LiveRe comments system</span><br><span class="line"># You can get your uid from https://livere.com/insight/myCode (General web site)</span><br><span class="line">livere_uid: # &lt;your_uid&gt; # 换成实际的uid</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="来必力uid获取"><a href="#来必力uid获取" class="headerlink" title="来必力uid获取"></a>来必力uid获取</h2><p><a href="https://www.livere.com/apply">livere</a><br>安装，首次安装需登录，然后注册新建博客站点，再次验证就可安装，得到uid</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 来必力安装代码uid</span><br><span class="line">&lt;livere-comment client-id=&quot;jdeMFmho8Q7pdnjlf1Ff&quot;&gt;&lt;/livere-comment&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script type=&quot;module&quot; src=&quot;https://www.livere.org/livere-widget.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>改动：1、active: livere 2、livere_uid: your_uid</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="各评论系统选择"><a href="#各评论系统选择" class="headerlink" title="各评论系统选择"></a>各评论系统选择</h2><p><img src="/images/comment_fig.png" alt="评论系统选择"></p>
<hr>
<h1 id="开启git评论"><a href="#开启git评论" class="headerlink" title="开启git评论"></a>开启git评论</h1><h2 id="原代码段"><a href="#原代码段" class="headerlink" title="原代码段"></a>原代码段</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Gitalk</span><br><span class="line"># For more information: https://gitalk.github.io</span><br><span class="line">gitalk:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: false</span><br><span class="line">  github_id: # GitHub repo owner</span><br><span class="line">  repo: # Repository name to store issues</span><br><span class="line">  client_id: # GitHub Application Client ID</span><br><span class="line">  client_secret: # GitHub Application Client Secret</span><br><span class="line">  admin_user: # GitHub repo owner and collaborators, only these guys can initialize gitHub issues</span><br><span class="line">  distraction_free_mode: true # Facebook-like distraction free mode</span><br><span class="line">  # When the official proxy is not available, you can change it to your own proxy address</span><br><span class="line">  proxy: https://cors-anywhere.azm.workers.dev/https://github.com/login/oauth/access_token # This is official proxy address</span><br><span class="line">  # Gitalk&#x27;s display language depends on user&#x27;s browser or system environment</span><br><span class="line">  # If you want everyone visiting your site to see a uniform language, you can set a force language value</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: en | es-ES | fr | ru | zh-CN | zh-TW</span><br><span class="line">  language:</span><br><span class="line">  # If you want to customize the content of the initialized Issue, please edit the body parameter.</span><br><span class="line">  # For example:</span><br><span class="line">  # body: Comments for post $&#123;title&#125;, see $&#123;url&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  body:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="创建"><a href="#创建" class="headerlink" title="创建"></a>创建</h2><ul>
<li>申请 Gitalk 必须的 client_id &#x2F;client_secret<br>Gitalk 需要 GitHub 第三方授权，必须创建&#x2F;注册一个 OAuth App<br><a href="https://github.com/settings/applications/new">OAuth App</a></li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 注册OAuth App页面配置</span><br><span class="line">Applacation name #任意，无须和github名一致</span><br><span class="line">Homepage URL # 必须与博客地址一致</span><br><span class="line">Application description #任意，描述词</span><br><span class="line">Authorization callback URL # 必须与博客地址一致</span><br><span class="line">Enable Device Flow # 不用勾选</span><br><span class="line">Register application #点击创建，即可获得client_ID和client_secret(密钥)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="git评论配置"><a href="#git评论配置" class="headerlink" title="git评论配置"></a>git评论配置</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gitalk:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  github_id: lan666-y           # GitHub用户名</span><br><span class="line">  repo: lan666-y.github.io      # 存评论的仓库名</span><br><span class="line">  client_id: 刚拿到的Client ID</span><br><span class="line">  client_secret: 刚生成的Client Secret</span><br><span class="line">  admin_user: lan666-y          # GitHub用户名</span><br><span class="line">  distraction_free_mode: true</span><br><span class="line">  proxy: https://cors-anywhere.azm.workers.dev/https://github.com/login/oauth/access_token</span><br><span class="line">  language: zh-CN               # 强制中文</span><br><span class="line">  body: 文章《$&#123;title&#125;》评论，地址：$&#123;url&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h1 id="开启busuanzi统计"><a href="#开启busuanzi统计" class="headerlink" title="开启busuanzi统计"></a>开启busuanzi统计</h1><h2 id="在配置文件中搜索busuanzi，启用true"><a href="#在配置文件中搜索busuanzi，启用true" class="headerlink" title="在配置文件中搜索busuanzi，启用true"></a>在配置文件中搜索busuanzi，启用true</h2><h2 id="显示文字解释"><a href="#显示文字解释" class="headerlink" title="显示文字解释"></a>显示文字解释</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 打开配置文件</span><br><span class="line">\blog\themes\next\layout\_partials\footer.njk</span><br><span class="line"># 注意在冒号后有一个空格</span><br><span class="line">在对应代码前加上&quot;本站总访问人数:&quot;和&quot;本站总访问量:&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/images/busuanzi_fig.png" alt="busuanzi_fig"></p>
]]></content>
  </entry>
